:
End of file.
:c                     更改1.的内容
  1  chan是大帅哥..
:.
:x
"u/c/chan/super" 1 lines 16 bytes
Exit from ed.
/u/c/chan> more super
chan是大帅哥..   你就可以看到你更改的内容了...
